title: The Travel Show: Countries A-H
description:
On episode 368, we debut a new series: "The Travel Show." This series we list and learn about countries in alphabetical order, with the occasional nonsenical ramble thrown in there. It's very similar to "Double Rainbow," but with countries rather than colors. Enjoy!
